 />\n北方人今日發唔到音，所以變咗做今天，然後就變成&quot;書面語&quot;"},{"pid":"546b75854261378384e4e63b2a4c0e79266c92ec","tid":320435,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"X界原種"},{"pid":"c9cd3202bfc07330a385430b78e9bb4b9e10149a","tid":320435,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飛的</blockquote><br />\n連登已經有人死撐 &quot;打的&quot; 係香港本地話"},{"pid":"415573e31b23e7e242334ae5c94263ec4c30eb52","tid":320435,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"英文跟音譯中文都計？"},{"pid":"cb142c18f4c210d0f3f981ec32f0e27e5dd36033","tid":320435,"uid":2089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9fd539afdefd45b7a5257d20c1616e68bd12913a","tid":320435,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a5da450878d41b7e2aa13b1ba42265ea0b8ac1e","tid":320435,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4931ee864b21309eae1b67294daadedba4edfa0","tid":320435,"uid":22029,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"耳筒 耳機兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有今天係書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面都係白話黎,你書寫係唔會另一方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BTW大陸都係口講會講另一方面"},{"pid":"4bf039a890c33e5f6a76084db18dd374184a2e45","tid":320435,"uid":70264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:48:09.000Z","msg":"「中文」係共產詞彙，係漢字。<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫人「你都係講返中文啦」。係講返「廣東話」/「香港話」。<br />\n<br />\n一個講潮州話，一個講廣東話，雙方唔明對方講咩，算唔算係識講同一種語言，同樣識講「中文」？"},{"pid":"00f54932855e895763e6ea71b1d079b8af965e75","tid":320435,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最恐怖唔係依d字入侵<br />\n而係你用左 俾人屌 然後仲死撐</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n最常用咪話係「白話」同「書面語」囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話咩一直都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩廣東話就係有「書面語」㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本冇一個可以成功用邏輯反駁點解有啲字係終日唔用亦唔會講，但就會係「書面語」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反駁唔到根本就係大中華統一文字嘅手法"},{"pid":"138241f5630beb6b2c0e46338f4121c0919c6929","tid":320435,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吊打係支那用詞，意思係你俾人屈機屈到好似以前農村體罰俾人攞繩吊住嚟打咁，後尾傳到過台灣成班文盲台狗以為吊字係殘體就將吊轉做繁體攪到成個意思無左，之後香港班傻仔見到台仔用自己又跟住用，仲要以為個字係台灣發源，真係笑死我, 用支那語言本身已經衰，仲要跟住個錯嘅嚟用</span></span></blockquote><br />\n舐台撚/港柒邏輯：台灣都用=唔係蝗語"},{"pid":"50958eff5d5c5bcc8d3420287d5d92330c0bd301","tid":320435,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"負累o唔ok?"}]}